\begin_inset Formula $\theta$
\end_inset

 is 
\begin_inset Formula $[a,b]$
\end_inset

.
 Then, 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
|a|\ge\frac{b}{n}.
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

